He’s a wonderful Savior to me.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}He’s a Friend so true, so patient and so kind,
He’s a wonderful Savior to me;
Everything I need in Him I always find,
He’s a wonderful Savior to me.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}He is always near to comfort and to cheer,
He’s a wonderful Savior to me;
He forgives my sins, He dries my every tear,
He’s a wonderful Savior to me.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Dearer grows the love of Jesus day by day,
He’s a wonderful Savior to me;
Sweeter is His grace while pressing on my way,
He’s a wonderful Savior to me.{/lang-eng}
